    {
      "id": 56971771206809,
      "type": "Comment",
      "author_id": 9977129389337,
      "body": "Need assistance from L3 team:\n\nCase: Product weight updates in Shopify not reflected in the app\n\nDetails:\nA $49 Premium plan MCSL customer has updated the weights for 3 products in Shopify. However, these changes are not reflected in the app, which is resulting in higher shipping rates.\n\n\nAll 3 products are updated to 0.3 oz in Shopify, but in the app they are showing 0.9 lbs (15 oz).\n\nAffected Products:\n\n- Keita Prints 109 Snack Time PRINT by Keita Takahashi\nSKU: 8BIT-8133-114\n- Keita Prints 110 Lunch Time PRINT by Keita Takahashi\nSKU: 8BIT-8133-115\n- Keita Prints 111 Tired of Adventure PRINT by Keita Takahashi\nSKU: 8BIT-8133-116\nI have attached the Shopify product PDF for your reference. The customer is not comfortable using the appointment link.\n\nCould you please check and update/sync the product weights from your end?\n\nExpected Result:\nProduct weight changes made in Shopify should be reflected correctly in the app, and shipping rates should be calculated based on the updated weights.\n\nStore Details:\nStore URL –  iam8bit.myshopify.com\nAccount ID – 522db151-491b-4342-9e3f-4d54c5dad8c5\n\n ![](https://pluginhive.zendesk.com/attachments/token/ccUWbJViBqtd8nOlK6GoTqarv/?name=image.png)",
      "html_body": "<div class=\"zd-comment\" dir=\"auto\">Need assistance from L3 team:<br>&nbsp;<br>Case: Product weight updates in Shopify not reflected in the app<br>&nbsp;<br>Details:<br>A $49 Premium plan MCSL customer has updated the weights for 3 products in Shopify. However, these changes are not reflected in the app, which is resulting in higher shipping rates.<br>&nbsp;<br><br>All 3 products are updated to 0.3 oz in Shopify, but in the app they are showing 0.9 lbs (15 oz).<br>&nbsp;<br>Affected Products:<br><ul dir=\"auto\"><li>Keita Prints 109 Snack Time PRINT by Keita Takahashi<br>SKU: 8BIT-8133-114</li><li>Keita Prints 110 Lunch Time PRINT by Keita Takahashi<br>SKU: 8BIT-8133-115</li><li>Keita Prints 111 Tired of Adventure PRINT by Keita Takahashi<br>SKU: 8BIT-8133-116</li></ul>I have attached the Shopify product PDF for your reference. The customer is not comfortable using the appointment link.<br>&nbsp;<br>Could you please check and update/sync the product weights from your end?<br>&nbsp;<br>Expected Result:<br>Product weight changes made in Shopify should be reflected correctly in the app, and shipping rates should be calculated based on the updated weights.<br>&nbsp;<br>Store Details:<br>Store URL – &nbsp;<a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"http://iam8bit.myshopify.com\">iam8bit.myshopify.com</a><br>Account ID – 522db151-491b-4342-9e3f-4d54c5dad8c5<br>&nbsp;<br><span style=\"opacity: 1;\"><img src=\"https://pluginhive.zendesk.com/attachments/token/ccUWbJViBqtd8nOlK6GoTqarv/?name=image.png\"></span><br></div>",
      "plain_body": "Need assistance from L3 team:\n&nbsp;\nCase: Product weight updates in Shopify not reflected in the app\n&nbsp;\nDetails:\nA $49 Premium plan MCSL customer has updated the weights for 3 products in Shopify. However, these changes are not reflected in the app, which is resulting in higher shipping rates.\n&nbsp;\n\nAll 3 products are updated to 0.3 oz in Shopify, but in the app they are showing 0.9 lbs (15 oz).\n&nbsp;\nAffected Products:\n  Keita Prints 109 Snack Time PRINT by Keita Takahashi\nSKU: 8BIT-8133-114  Keita Prints 110 Lunch Time PRINT by Keita Takahashi\nSKU: 8BIT-8133-115  Keita Prints 111 Tired of Adventure PRINT by Keita Takahashi\nSKU: 8BIT-8133-116  I have attached the Shopify product PDF for your reference. The customer is not comfortable using the appointment link.\n&nbsp;\nCould you please check and update/sync the product weights from your end?\n&nbsp;\nExpected Result:\nProduct weight changes made in Shopify should be reflected correctly in the app, and shipping rates should be calculated based on the updated weights.\n&nbsp;\nStore Details:\nStore URL – &nbsp;iam8bit.myshopify.com\nAccount ID – 522db151-491b-4342-9e3f-4d54c5dad8c5\n&nbsp;",
